White Noise + Privacy Policy

Effective Date: 12-12-2025

This Policy explains how Akhtars IT Solutions collects, uses, and protects information when you use the White Noise + App.

1. Data Controller

Akhtars IT Solutions, Pakistan, is responsible for managing your data.

2. Information We Collect

We may collect the following:

| Category                     | Type                                           | How We Collect                         | Why We Collect                                                    |
| ---------------------------- | ---------------------------------------------- | -------------------------------------- | ----------------------------------------------------------------- |
| Personally Identifiable Data | Username, email                                | Provided during account creation       | Account access, notifications                                     |
| User Content                 | Self recordings, profile images                | Uploaded by you from gallery or camera | To save, store, and display your custom sounds and profile images |
| Usage Data                   | Sounds played, session duration, features used | Automatic app tracking                 | Improve app performance and recommendations                       |
| Device Data                  | Device model, OS, App version                  | Collected automatically                | Troubleshooting, compatibility                                    |

Note: Profile images can be uploaded from the device gallery or captured using the camera.

3. Use of Collected Data

We use your data to:

Provide and maintain app features

Personalize your experience

Send service notices and support messages

Analyze performance and improve features

Meet legal requirements

4. Sharing and Disclosure

We do not sell your data. We may share your information only:

With service providers such as cloud hosting and analytics tools

When legally required

During business transfers such as mergers

5. Data Security and Storage

We apply reasonable security measures, including encryption.
Your data may be stored on secure cloud servers.

6. Data Retention

We keep your information while your account remains active.
When you delete your account, we begin deleting your information within a reasonable period, unless required to retain it by law.

7. Your Rights

You may request to:

View your personal data

Correct inaccurate information

Delete your account and stored recordings or profile images

Opt out of marketing messages

8. Childrenâ€™s Privacy

The App is not intended for anyone under 13. If we discover data from a minor, we will remove it.

9. Updates to the Policy

We may update this Policy. The revised version will include a new Effective Date.

